{
  "stem": "25348.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as I lay fully dressed on my bunk, I hear my name, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and someone calling out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carolina, you have a visitor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who could it be?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Gestapo?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Suddenly, a wrinkled face of a woman became visible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this woman--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why I told you it has a connection-- this woman told me she is Frau Moebius, the wife of that German supervisor from Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] What happened, I must break to tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He initiated a search.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not for a Jew, but for a Polish employee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't have taken any notice-- the staff at the labor office in Poland would not have taken-- I was registered there as a legitimate Pole-- they wouldn't have taken notice of a Pole searching for another Pole.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this was a German citizen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everything has to be done by lists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even lists went off to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was a transport to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] These Moebiuses had a daughter-in-law who was in charge, in her district, of the-- of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's labor supply office.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she helped her in-laws to trace me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't know whether this woman who came to see me, whether she was foe or friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I wondered how she found me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I wondered, as if guessing my question, she told me that her husband initiated a-- that search.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And her daughter-in-law, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Theresa, ?] narrowed it down to this place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she came to see me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she asked me, are you well enough to travel?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wondered what was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wanted to take me to her house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't have a house-- an apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
